Installation instructions for library MatrixAbstractLayer
----------------------------------------------

It is recommended to create a specific directory to install this package.
mkdir build
cd build
../configure [OPTIONS]
make 
make install

[OPTION] (see also configure.ac)
--with-boost=PATH_TO_BOOST
or
--with-VNL=PATH_TO_VNL
or 
--with-lapack=PATH_TO_LAPACK

--with-t3d if you want to use t3d for rigid-body transformations. Alternatively,
           a local implementation will be used.
